== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 30 Ugushyingo 1976 i Attredgeville, umujyi wa Pretoria, [[Afurika y'Epfo]] mu muryango w'abanyapolitiki. Yarezwe na nyirakuru abifashijwemo n'abasaza ba Pan Africanist Congress of Azania (PAC). <ref>https://www.monatelly.com/aubrey-poolo-on-his-upbringing-and-five-fingers-for-marseilles-role/</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Akiri muto cyane, yinjiye muri gahunda ya tereviziyo ''Legae la bana'' . Muri 2010, yakinnye bwa mbere muri firime  ''[[:en:Life,_Above_All|Life, Above All]]''. Filime yerekanwe mu gice cya Un Certain Regard mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Cannes 2010 . <ref>http://www.festival-cannes.com/en/archives/ficheFilm/id/11023168/year/2010.html</ref> Yatoranijwe kandi nk'iyinjira muri Afurika y'Epfo muri Filime nziza y'ururimi rw'amahanga mu bihembo bya 83 <ref>http://www.oscars.org/press/pressreleases/2010/20101013a.html</ref> hanyuma ikora urutonde rwa nyuma rwatangajwe muri Mutarama 2011. <ref name="Oscar Shortlist">http://www.oscars.org/press/pressreleases/2011/20110119.html</ref> Intsinzi ya firime, yatoranijwe muri televiziyo yo muri Amerika yo muri 2017 ya ''Madiba'' kugira ngo agire uruhare ruto.

Muri 2017, yakinnye cyane 'Unathi' muri firime yo muri Afrika yepfo yuburengerazuba bwa firime yitwa ''Fingers for Marseilles'' iyobowe na Michael Matthews . Nyuma yaje kwerekanwa mu gice cya Discovery mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya firime rya Toronto 2017 kandi ryishimiwe cyane. <ref>http://www.thewrap.com/toronto-film-festival-adds-international-films-angelina-jolie-javier-bardem/</ref>

